snippet.title: Abalone - Trailer
snippet.description: Discover the all new digital version of the classic two-player abstract strategy board game, Abalone. Move your player marbles strategically to push six of your opponents' marbles off the edge of the board. The key to success in Abalone is patience and wisdom - some players will master it, will you be one? Abalone's practice mode will help make it so! Once you are ready to compete, pick up your marbles and game on!
